{"type": "article", "id": 2801, "title": "多功能卡尺笔", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-13T07:17:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232603asB67pTNSr0tVKJ9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t德国文具品牌 Cleo Skribent 已有 69 年历史，凭借其多功能的应用、精细的制作工艺以及流畅的书写效果，深受不少建筑师、设计师与工程师等人群的喜爱。日前，Cleo Skribent 新推出了一款全新的 Messograf 多功能卡尺笔，笔身由银色的镀铬黄铜金属打造，除了满足最基础的圆珠笔功能以外，这支笔还配有游标卡尺、直尺与量规等功能。定价 46 美元，<a href=\"http://store.hypebeast.com/cn/brands/messograf-caliper-pen/silver-messograf-caliper-ballpoint-pen\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232601FUaxSf362X8D5nd4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232601p0F3qjgLOevwsUN5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232602oYHNnqyuFCib9M26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232602hKUJt2nLmo04r1d9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}